name: Human rat metabolism
tagline: Reconciled reconstructions of rat and human metabolism tailored for toxicological studies
body:
### Download models
Get the latest versions of iRno and iHsa at http://bme.virginia.edu/csbl/downloads
The manuscript associated with code in this repository is currently under review at Molecular Systems Biology.
If you have any questions, please email edik blais (emb8ab at virginia dot edu)
